    <domain>software-developer</domain>
    <summary>Extract multi-step business workflows from fat controllers into app/services/&lt;BoundedContext&gt;/&lt;Action&gt;Service classes with a single call method that returns ServiceResult (success/failure).</summary>
    <tags>
      <tag>rails</tag>
      <tag>service-objects</tag>
      <tag>patterns</tag>
      <tag>refactoring</tag>
      <tag>transactions</tag>
    </tags>
